headline: Dollar Tree to Host National Hiring Week, Offering Thousands of Career Opportunities Nationwide
summary: CHESAPEAKE, Va., September 11, 2025--Dollar Tree, Inc. (NASDAQ: DLTR), today announced its stores will host a National Hiring Week taking place Sept. 14 - 20, where it plans to hire thousands of associates across more than 9,000 stores nationwide. Open positions include a variety of part-time and full-time roles, including store managers, assistant store managers, and customer service associates.
